    <p>
      <b><font size="5">THE WORLD OF EARTH</font></b>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
<font NAME="SansSerif" BOLD="true"/>
<node TEXT="OVERVIEW" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1433196932" CREATED="1333245526003" MODIFIED="1359771206112" COLOR="#000000">
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="12" BOLD="true"/>
<node ID="ID_264164721" CREATED="1333245530038" MODIFIED="1334708095390" COLOR="#000000"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <b><u>OVERVIEW</u></b>
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;The United States fell after a second civil war over political heat and the people's anger. Amidst this war, a strange thing happened. A radient bright light washed over the land from east to west. When it was gone, everything that was powered by electricity stopped functioning never to return again. This plunged the war torn states into a dark age where murder and greed ran the streets. There was no order.
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;Then came the dawn of <b>Sinvin</b>, a strange oily substance that could be mined from harvested newfound crystals throughout the land. This restarted the economy but it was never what it use to be. America was sent back to the days of steam power.
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;After several hundred years, the roads became abandoned and bridges fell. New smaller roads were put into place. There was an order to things.
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; <b>The rich class:</b>&#xa0;Those who controlled cities with power of crystals.
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; <b>The poor class:</b>&#xa0;Those who worked the mines, factories and fields.
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;There was no central government any longer. States were their own country and cities were their own power so long as they paid the state country.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="People and Religion" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_157078205" CREATED="1333245538741" MODIFIED="1359771202502" COLOR="#000000">
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="12" BOLD="true"/>
<node ID="ID_1420788494" CREATED="1333245539207" MODIFIED="1334708099594" COLOR="#000000"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <b><u>PEOPLE AND RELIGION</u></b>
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;Earth has many different people and religions. In the post united states where the story takes place, the people has lost hope. Religion in Gods are all but extinct. The thought of a deity in the post dark ere poses anger and hatred towards any who speak of it.
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;There are a few countries in the North Americas where religion is less restricted&#xa0;but they are hard to find and not well broadcasted.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="Structure of Government" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_136483833" CREATED="1333245643113" MODIFIED="1359771201502" COLOR="#000000">
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="12" BOLD="true"/>
<node ID="ID_683528090" CREATED="1333245820468" MODIFIED="1334708103658" COLOR="#000000"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <b><u>STRUCTURE OF GOVERNMENT</u></b>
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;America has no centeral government. The government is run by the state countries. Each state country makes their own laws though they are usually similar to each other.
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;There is a central capital where the countries' affairs are discussed and dealt with. They are still elected to office but hold very little say in a person's life. The capital's power extends only to the countries well being. A person's life is in the care of a city or town. If the city itself cannot deal with the person, only then will the person be transfered over to the government to pass judgement.
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;This holds the same in all areas of life of a country whether it be a person's life or job placement. The structure of government holds that the state head has no power. The city has the power.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="Cultures and Lands" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_431170779" CREATED="1333245665599" MODIFIED="1359771200221" COLOR="#000000">
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="12" BOLD="true"/>
<node ID="ID_546146690" CREATED="1333247362469" MODIFIED="1334708173452" COLOR="#000000"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <u><b>CULTURES AND LANDS </b></u>
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;The United States is split into many cultures. Since the reformation of the Americas in the Crystal Age, a new culture of people emerged. These are a fanatical people who are more in line of a cult. They worship the sun.
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;For thousands of years, the cultures of the United States were very diverse.
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;When the country fell and state countries replaced the union, a pilgrimage of various people migrated to form towns where the people had the same ideals and customs.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="Transportation" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_698974524" CREATED="1333247425269" MODIFIED="1359771203534" COLOR="#000000">
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="12" BOLD="true"/>
<node ID="ID_47493936" CREATED="1333247510133" MODIFIED="1334708132752" COLOR="#000000"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <u><b>TRANSPORTATION </b></u>
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;For the longest time after the United States fell, there was no transportation of any kind. This was a secondary cause of economic failure. Without cars or any type of motorized transportation, there was no way to get to the cities that were now days and weeks away.
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;The steam engine train was brought back into commision 100 years later. The railroad system became the first interstate job that brought the economy back.
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;From state country to state country, the railroad recrossed America.
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;When <b>Sinvin</b>&#xa0;was introduced and the properties of the new crystal was discovered, it brought in a new era of economy as well as transportation.
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;<b>Airships</b>&#xa0;were the new invention of transportation. With the power of the crystal, it's power was harnessed to fuel airships, ships built to fly. With the <b>fusion of steam and crystal</b>, the airship became the dominant transportation vehicle. It was faster than the steam engine and was constantly being reinvented.
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; <b>Airship Yards</b>&#xa0;were built and a new Era of transportation began.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="Economy" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1044292239" CREATED="1333247688855" MODIFIED="1359771204846" COLOR="#000000">
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="12" BOLD="true"/>
<node ID="ID_1013250432" CREATED="1333247736560" MODIFIED="1334708137315" COLOR="#000000"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <u><b>ECONOMY </b></u>
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;The fall of the United States collapsed the economy to a complete standstill for over 75 years. In this period of time, much of the population of the new state countries died from various causes relating from malnutrition and sickness.
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;When the steam engine train was finally recommisioned, it brought the first real jobs to a crippled land. From railway crews to building stations and maintaining, the train system restarted the defunct economy. With the rail system now connecting cities to cities, it brought in customers.
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;It wasn't until Sinvin was introduced by strange traders that a new era began. The properties of Sinvin in it's oil form was energy for a multitude of things. It could heal diseases, make things last longer, and give a longer life to the steam engines.
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;It wasn't until a new kind of crystal was discovered that it's properties became apparent. It's nature to give off energy was first examined extensively before realizing just how powerful the internal core of the crystal was. This then began the invention of the next major vehicle. The Airship.
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;With the combined fusion of steam and crystal core, the airship was the next major invention of travel.
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;With this new found power and invention, mining companies sprouted up overnight.
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;The economy boosted again as the next era began as the Crystal Era.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="THE WORLD OF EXODUS" LOCALIZED_STYLE_REF="AutomaticLayout.level.root" POSITION="left" ID="ID_1090958577" CREATED="1409300609620" MODIFIED="1671241434146" VGAP_QUANTITY="3 pt">
<font BOLD="true"/>
<node TEXT="MAIN OVERVIEW" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1889210993" CREATED="1333248202550" MODIFIED="1335896668164" COLOR="#000000">
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="12" BOLD="true"/>
<node ID="ID_568205309" CREATED="1333249461017" MODIFIED="1334708028013" COLOR="#000000"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <u><b>OVERVIEW </b></u>
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;Exodus co-exists with Earth as part of the 1st House of Dragonborn. Whereas Earth is where humans originated, Exodus is where magic of imagination and dreams began. All of mythology came from Exodus' vast Ancient cultures from dragons and dryads to the centaurs and faries.
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;They often crossed over into our world yet still masked by the Hidden Realm of <b>Myra.</b>
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;Over the course of human history on Exodus, the magic that once permiated all of Exodus slowly faded as Ancients departed behind the <b>Tera Veil</b>.
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;Each major country of Elise and Eden were first the <b>High Seat of Ancient</b>&#xa0;races.
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;In the 5th Age, Ancients saw how much man wanted the power of magic. But with the White Council's greed came a shadow of darkness. This was choking the magic essence of the Ancients and destroying the world.
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;As a whole, the Ancients began to rethink their abandoning the 1st Tera of Exodus.
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;War was on the horizon.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node ID="ID_97510404" CREATED="1333822006666" MODIFIED="1334708021282" COLOR="#000000" VSHIFT_QUANTITY="-5 px"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <b><u>9 gods of Exodus </u></b>
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <b>1. Yilos -</b>&#xa0;sun god (Early Spring- a time to worship fearfully and plant fields/ Yilos is the high god)
    </p>
    <p>
      <b>2. Kata -</b>&#xa0;spirit god (Late Spring- a time of pilgrimage to pray for good crops and other things)
    </p>
    <p>
      <b>3. Diea -</b>&#xa0;twin moon goddess (below) Interchangable when speaking about Summer.
    </p>
    <p>
      <b>4. Miea -</b>&#xa0;twin moon goddess (Early to Late Summer- a time of festivities to pay homage to the moon gods in order to appease their wrath; Blood Moon is the time of the Mordis Gal, the night of sacrifice because the gods are angry. Blood Moon can come at any time of the year and conflicts with the worship of other gods, especially Yilos, the high god. But he never seems to mind. The rule of Mordis Gal is to kill someone you love to show your loyalty to the moon gods to appease their wrath)
    </p>
    <p>
      <b>5. Fiross -</b>&#xa0;fire god (Early Fall- A time to make ammends, fellowship and pray for a good harvest)
    </p>
    <p>
      <b>6. Ousil -</b>&#xa0;water goddess (Late Fall- a time to pray to the god of water who sustains life)
    </p>
    <p>
      <b>7. Rawtis -</b>&#xa0;Earth god (Harvest Season- A time to harvest crops and pray for yielding of much with festivities)
    </p>
    <p>
      <b>8. Mayu -</b>&#xa0;wind goddess (End of the year- a time of foretelling; a season of heavy wind means the next year will be harsh, a season of mild wind means Mayu is content and won't argue with the other gods making the next year pleasent)
    </p>
    <p>
      <b>9. Tarris -</b>&#xa0;traveling star god (No season- The feared god that contends with Yilos for dominion over Exodus. By day Yilos rules, by night, Tarris rules and is the god of the Elves.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
