<node TEXT="Count" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_781915020" CREATED="1335985480365" MODIFIED="1335985611592">
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="12" BOLD="true"/>
<node ID="ID_1062483528" CREATED="1335985514592" MODIFIED="1335985607811"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <b><u>Count Simbar Rolis</u></b>
    </p>
    <p>
      <b>Overview: </b>Rolis is a converted pirate who once roamed the Drysin Sea. Now he holds the title of governor granted by King Fester. Over the years, Simbar Rolis has managed to use his years as a pirate to his advantage gaining favor and allies where others could not.
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;Cabol quickly became one of Calmone's most important and wealthy provinces.
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;Rolis' skill in trade and the atmosphere he created for the major cities on the sea made port cities explode.
    </p>
    <p>
      &#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;It was also one way to bypass all other countries that wanted to tax everyone for going through their land on trade business.
    </p>
    <p>
      <b>Personality: </b>Rolis had a friendly way about him with everyone. For his hefty size and background, at times people forgot he use to be a pirate. He was one with the people.
    </p>
    <p>
      <b>Appearance: </b>Simbar Rolis has a heavy set frame. His face is round and his blonde hair covers him splitting down the middle. He wears spectacles over a jolly happy face.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="Viscounts" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_938676535" CREATED="1335985627243" MODIFIED="1335985683230">
