    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>Do you like interacting with large groups of people? </u></b></font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      yes, I love the interaction
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>Are you generally introverted or extroverted? </u></b></font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      extroverted
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
