<node TEXT="3. Social Relationships" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1486977158" CREATED="1378944027555" MODIFIED="1379977429376" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#ccccff">
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="12" BOLD="true"/>
<node ID="ID_481404117" CREATED="1379441094915" MODIFIED="1379977454590" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#dcd0a0"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <font size="3"><u><b>ROMANCE</b></u>&#xa0;</font>
    </p>
    <p>
      <font size="3">Ravage was never one to settle down with a woman. He has sworn to himself to never let a woman into his life. This has held true until he meets Tari Alcorin. Her stubborness gets to him and he finds her a challenge. </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      <font size="3"><b>Martial Status:</b>&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;S </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      <font size="3"><b>Friends:</b>&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;Ravage </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      <font size="3"><b>Allies:</b>&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;none </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      <font size="3"><b>Enemies:</b>&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;Everyone </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      <font size="3">________________________________ </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <font size="3"><u><b>PERSONAL RELATIONSHIPS</b></u>&#xa0;</font>
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <font size="3"><u><b>Who is the most important person and why? </b></u></font>
    </p>
    <p>
      <font size="3">At first the only one to look after was himself. He has done this forever. When Tari enters the picture however, Ravage finds his loyalty shifting towards the girl as stubborn as she is. She has a tendancy to get herself in trouble. Ravage finds himself watching over her and after awhile, long dormant emotions begin to stir causing him to be protective of Tari. </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      <font size="3"><u><b>Who is the person you respect the most? Despise the most? Why? </b></u></font>
    </p>
    <p>
      <font size="3">There are only two people Ravage truly respects. That is Vale Sherwin and Teldan Jerlock. They were the ones who saved him from himself remaining in the darkness. They took a chance on him when no others would.</font>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="4. History" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_530939546" CREATED="1378944332997" MODIFIED="1379976250386" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#ccccff">
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="12" BOLD="true"/>
<node ID="ID_1893504430" CREATED="1378945178228" MODIFIED="1379976869239" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#dcd0a0"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <font size="3"><b><u>Childhood:</u></b> </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      <font size="3">Ravage doesn't remember his childhood. It's been too long ago. </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      <font size="3"><b><u>Teenage Years:</u></b>&#xa0; </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      <font size="3">Brief glimpses are all he can remember. These glimpses are of pain. </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      <font size="3"><b><u>Adulthood: </u></b></font>
    </p>
    <p>
      <font size="3">Most of Ravage's adulthood is remembered as that of a vicious prince who would go out and terrorize the world. He would follow his father's commands to a fault and be remembered as the Dark Lord in history. His father was always behind the scenes while Ravage made himself known to be a name feared by everyone. His vicious past was put to many different legends and poems to remind all that there was a dark lord not to forget. </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <font size="3">Through divine intervension and Ravage's sudden feeling of emotion, he was led on a dangerous path leading him away from his father and to a truth that would alter his very life. </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <font size="3">Now Ravage walks in the shadows hiding from every living person as well as his own father's spies.</font>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node ID="ID_364717692" CREATED="1378945305588" MODIFIED="1380591710048" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#dcd0a0"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>LIFE - IN DETAIL </u></b></font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>1 How would you describe your life overall</u>? </b></font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3">dark and depressing </font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>2 What is your most memorable moment? </u></b></font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3">if talking about the past, the child prisoner and her unwavering belief in Elyon. There is no memorable moment now, just a face and that is Tari. </font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>3 What has been the most important event in your life</u>? </b></font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3">The change from evil to good </font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>4 What do you consider your greatest achievement? </u></b></font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3">none. life was evil and there was no achieving in this. </font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>5 What is your number one regret? </u></b></font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3">being evil </font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>6 When were you the most afraid?</u>&#xa0; </b></font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3">when he lost his powers </font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>7 What is your greatest fear? Why?</u>&#xa0; </b></font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3">Failure because it would show weakness and he has always been strong </font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>8 What is the most honorable or &#x201c;good&#x201d; thing you&#x2019;ve ever done?</u>&#xa0; </b></font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3">surrendering the evil life </font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>9 What is the most &#x201c;evil&#x201d; thing you have ever done?</u>&#xa0; </b></font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3">too many to count </font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>10 Have you ever been in love?&#xa0;If so, describe what happened.</u>&#xa0; </b></font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3">Tari - the event is hard to describe because of the walls put up. Over the course of two years she crept into my cold heart and melted away my wall towards her. </font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>11 Do you have a notorious or celebrated ancestor/relative?</u>&#xa0; </b></font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3">My father the Emperor of Night</font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>11a Does that affect you? </u></b></font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3">Yes it affects me. my namesake is a burden knowing my past is linked with him. I hide because of&#xa0;&#xa0;this fact </font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>12 Do you have any secrets? If so, what are they?</u>&#xa0; </b></font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3">my secret is that i still crave the evil</font>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="5. Personality" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1537053415" CREATED="1378944362848" MODIFIED="1379976766317" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#ccccff">
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="12" BOLD="true"/>
<node ID="ID_1848323726" CREATED="1378945407900" MODIFIED="1380592308502" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#dcd0a0"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>PERSONALITY</u></b>&#xa0; </font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>What three words would you use to best describe your personality?</u></b>&#xa0; </font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>What three words would others probably use to describe you?</u></b>&#xa0;</font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      emotionless, cold, struggling
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>Why are you risking your life to adventure?</u></b>&#xa0;</font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      to redeem myself from the evil I was a part of
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>Do you tend to argue with people or avoid conflict?</u></b>&#xa0;</font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      I avoid everything but if I have to I will make my point clear
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>Are you a listener or a talker?</u></b>&#xa0;</font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      listener
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>How long does it take for you to trust others?</u></b>&#xa0;</font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      a very long time. I dont trust anyone except a few
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>Do you hold grudges? </u></b></font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      I try not to
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>Do you tend to take on leadership roles in social situations?</u></b>&#xa0; </font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      no
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>Do you like interacting with large groups of people? </u></b></font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      no
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>Are you generally introverted or extroverted? </u></b></font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      introverted
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3">_______________________________________________________ </font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>PERSONAL EMOTIONS</u></b>&#xa0; </font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>What makes you sad? Happy? Mad? Why?</u></b>&#xa0;</font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      I don't particularly feel anything. But when I see the evil and how it affects people, I do tend to get involved because I know where it comes from. Tari makes me happy if that can be used to describe me. She is a light in my cold world
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>Do you have any biases or prejudices?</u></b>&#xa0;</font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      no
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>What do you think of love?</u></b>&#xa0;</font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      it is hard
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>Do you believe in self-sacrifice for the greater good?</u></b>&#xa0;</font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      I do a little. It is a debt I feel deeply about. I owe everyone my life. If there were a prison to hold me, I would be in it. But since there is none, I am my own prison.
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>If you could change one thing about yourself, what would it be?</u></b>&#xa0; </font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      I wouldn't change anything because I deserve my fate
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="6. Goals" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1473278678" CREATED="1378944405499" MODIFIED="1379976755307" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#ccccff">
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="12" BOLD="true"/>
<node ID="ID_274323138" CREATED="1378945748160" MODIFIED="1380592575711" BACKGROUND_COLOR="#dcd0a0"><richcontent TYPE="NODE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>GOALS</u></b>&#xa0;</font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>1 What are your goals?</u></b>&#xa0;</font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      to heal the land from my father's darkness
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>2 What goal do you most want to accomplish in your lifetime?</u></b>&#xa0;</font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      to bring the land I destroyed back to it's former glory
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>3 Where do you see yourself in five years? Ten years? Twenty years?</u></b>&#xa0; </font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      I don't concern myself with these things. I simply take one day at a time
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>4 If you could choose, how would you want to die?</u></b>&#xa0;</font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      a martyr of Elyon
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      <font size="3"><b><u>5 What is the one thing you would like to be remembered for after your death?</u></b>&#xa0; </font>
    </p>
    <p lang="en">
      I don't want to be remembered
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
